          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2196-v2-2196-v3-2196-v4-Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mince is cooking, combine your <strong>cornflour</strong> with 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[100ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[125ml] </span><strong>cold water </strong>in a bowl<strong> </strong>and give it a good whisk</p><p>Add your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>sticky stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2196-v2-2196-v3-2196-v4-Step-4-1-x200.jpg",
