          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2196-v2-2196-v3-2196-v4-Step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sticky beef & broccoli noodle stir-fry</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
